  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to GtkSourceViewmm</title>

    <para>
      The <application>GtksSourceViewmm</application> application is a C++
      wrapper for the <application>GtkSourceView</application> widget library.
    </para>

    &lfs70_checked;

